<h1>Infinitary Rewriting in Coq</h1>

<p>
My master project is concerned with a formalisation of the theory of
infinitary term <a href="http://rewriting.loria.fr/">rewriting</a>
in the <a href="http://coq.inria.fr/">Coq</a> proof assistant.
I am working on this with
<a href="http://www.cs.vu.nl/~diem/">Dimitri Hendriks</a>.
</p>

<p>
This page will (might?) be updated as we progress.
For now, maybe you are interested in some of the
<a href="http://www.citeulike.org/user/mvermaat/tag/master-project">literature</a>
related to the project.
</p>

<p>
If you have any thoughts on the subject, please feel free to
<a href="mailto:martijn@vermaat.name">share them</a> with me.
</p>

</body>

</html>
